description: A saxophone playing programmer that just loves music. I'm currently moving back to Stockholm where I hope to find time to finish some of my songs.

Markus Enochson is a pretty old Swedish guy from Stockholm. He has released a lot of records, some house a little techno and a few things you could not even guess. ”Right now I do music that I like, not really concerned about genres or distinction anymore.”
